<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id12255500-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777" identifier="/us/usc/t44/s1112"><num value="1112">§ 1112.</num><heading> Annual reports: type for reports of executive officers</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The annual reports of executive officers shall be printed in the same type and form as the report of the head of the department which it accompanies, unless otherwise ordered by the Joint Committee on Printing.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id12255501-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/620">Pub. L. 90–620</ref>, <date date="1968-10-22">Oct. 22, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/1263">82 Stat. 1263</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
